<!-- PROBLEM SECTION -->
<section class="section problem-section">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="slabel">Sound Familiar?</div>
    <h2>Planning a Kids' Party Shouldn't Eat <span class="grad">Your Whole Weekend</span></h2>
    <p class="sdesc">Coordinating carpools. Booking a venue. Tracking down waivers. Ordering pizza. Counting heads. Cleaning up. A typical group outing can swallow 10+ hours before the fun even starts.</p>
    <div class="pain-grid">
      <div class="pain-card">
        <div class="pain-x">😩</div>
        <h4>Venue Chaos</h4>
        <p>Juggling multiple reservations, deposits, and contacts just to make one party happen.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="pain-card">
        <div class="pain-x">🚗</div>
        <h4>Carpool Nightmare</h4>
        <p>Wrangling 10+ kids across multiple cars to multiple locations. Something always goes wrong.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="pain-card">
        <div class="pain-x">😤</div>
        <h4>Hidden Fees</h4>
        <p>The venue quote looked great until the wristbands, food minimums, and service charges hit.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="problem-answer">
      <div class="pa-icon">✅</div>
      <p>We handle all of it — so you get the credit and keep your Saturday.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- HOW IT WORKS -->
<section id="how-it-works" class="section hiw-section">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="slabel">The Itinerary</div>
    <h2>Here's Exactly <span class="grad">How the Day Works</span></h2>
    <p class="sdesc">Real times. Real activities. No guessing. Parents and kids know exactly what to expect from drop-off to pickup.</p>

    <div class="timeline">

      <div class="tl-step">
        <div class="tl-time">12:00 PM</div>
        <div class="tl-dot"><span>01</span></div>
        <div class="tl-content">
          <!-- Replace step1.jpg with a photo of kids arriving / check-in -->
          <img src="/images/step1.jpg" alt="Kids checking in at APEX BJJ" loading="lazy" class="tl-img"/>
          <div class="tl-body">
            <div class="tl-tag">📍 Meetup at APEX BJJ</div>
            <h3>Arrive &amp; Check In</h3>
            <p>Arrive and meet our team. We verify the guest list, hand out wristbands, and go over quick safety notes. Group photo before departure!</p>
            <ul class="tl-list">
              <li>Arrival &amp; check-in</li>
              <li>Boarding wristbands</li>
              <li>Safety instructions</li>
              <li>Group photo 📸</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="tl-step">
        <div class="tl-time">12:15 – 1:15 PM</div>
        <div class="tl-dot tl-dot-orange"><span>02</span></div>
        <div class="tl-content">
          <!-- Replace step2.jpg with a photo of kids on the party bus -->
          <img src="/images/step2.jpg" alt="Kids on VIP party bus Las Vegas" loading="lazy" class="tl-img"/>
          <div class="tl-body">
            <div class="tl-tag tl-tag-orange">🚌 Party Bus Cruise</div>
            <h3>The Party Starts on the Bus</h3>
            <p>Board the VIP bus for a high-energy 1-hour cruise. Music, glow accessories, games, and surprise activities. Chilled juice, water &amp; sodas on board.</p>
            <ul class="tl-list">
              <li>1-hour onboard party bus</li>
              <li>Sing &amp; dance to the party playlist</li>
              <li>Juices, water &amp; sodas included</li>
              <li>Games &amp; other surprises!</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="tl-step">
        <div class="tl-time">1:30 – 2:30 PM</div>
        <div class="tl-dot tl-dot-pink"><span>03</span></div>
        <div class="tl-content">
          <!-- Replace step3.jpg with a photo of kids jumping at Sky Zone -->
          <img src="/images/step3.jpg" alt="Kids jumping at Sky Zone Las Vegas" loading="lazy" class="tl-img"/>
          <div class="tl-body">
            <div class="tl-tag tl-tag-pink">🦘 Sky Zone</div>
            <h3>1 Hour of Pure Jump Time</h3>
            <p>Full access to Sky Zone's attractions during your dedicated hour. Everything is pre-arranged — no waiting in line, no sorting out wristbands. Our team keeps the schedule so everyone maximizes bounce time.</p>
            <ul class="tl-list">
              <li>1-hour dedicated freejump time</li>
              <li>All Sky Zone areas &amp; features</li>
              <li>Sky Zone grippy socks included</li>
              <li>Our team on-site throughout</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="tl-step">
        <div class="tl-time">2:30 – 3:30 PM</div>
        <div class="tl-dot tl-dot-teal"><span>04</span></div>
        <div class="tl-content">
          <!-- Replace step4.jpg with a photo of the pizza party -->
          <img src="/images/step4.jpg" alt="Kids pizza party Las Vegas" loading="lazy" class="tl-img"/>
          <div class="tl-body">
            <div class="tl-tag tl-tag-teal">🍕 Pizza Party</div>
            <h3>Private Pizza Party to Finish</h3>
            <p>Reserved private room, hot pizza, water &amp; soda. Your dedicated party host handles everything — seating, service, and cake time if you bring one.</p>
            <ul class="tl-list">
              <li>1-hour private party area</li>
              <li>Hot pizza + water &amp; soda</li>
              <li>Dedicated party host</li>
              <li>Bring a cake for birthdays! 🎂</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="tl-step tl-step-last">
        <div class="tl-time">3:30 PM</div>
        <div class="tl-dot tl-dot-blue"><span>✓</span></div>
        <div class="tl-content tl-content-end">
          <div class="tl-body">
            <div class="tl-tag tl-tag-blue">🏁 Parent Pickup at Sky Zone</div>
            <h3>Smooth, Supervised Handoff</h3>
            <p>Parents pick up at Sky Zone. Kids are only released to the parent or guardian on the approved list. Real-time updates sent to your phone throughout the day.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>

    <div class="hiw-cta">
      <a href="#pricing" class="btn-p">Book the Adventure →</a>
      <a href="tel:+17024830463" class="btn-g">📞 Call With Questions</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- WHAT'S INCLUDED -->
<section id="included" class="section inc-section">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="slabel">All-Inclusive</div>
    <h2>Everything Included. <span class="grad">No Surprises.</span></h2>
    <p class="sdesc">One flat price per child covers it all. No add-on fees sprung on you at checkout.</p>
    <div class="inc-grid">
      <div class="inc-card">
        <div class="inc-icon">🚌</div>
        <h4>Round-Trip Party Bus</h4>
        <p>Professional driver, upbeat music, glow accessories, and beverages onboard. The ride is part of the party.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="inc-card">
        <div class="inc-icon">🦘</div>
        <h4>Sky Zone Entry + Jump Time</h4>
        <p>1-hour dedicated session with full access to Sky Zone's attractions. Grippy socks included — no surprise fees at the door.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="inc-card">
        <div class="inc-icon">🍕</div>
        <h4>Private Pizza Party</h4>
        <p>Reserved room, hot pizza, water &amp; soda, and a dedicated party host for the full hour.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="inc-card">
        <div class="inc-icon">🎀</div>
        <h4>VIP Wristbands</h4>
        <p>Every child gets a wristband at check-in. Makes them feel like the VIPs they are — and keeps our team organized.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="inc-card">
        <div class="inc-icon">💰</div>
        <h4>All Gratuity Included</h4>
        <p>Driver tip and host gratuity are both built into your price. No awkward math at the end of the day.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="inc-card">
        <div class="inc-icon">📱</div>
        <h4>Real-Time Parent Updates</h4>
        <p>You get a message at every checkpoint — check-in, bus departure, venue arrival, and pickup time. Always in the loop.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="inc-callout">
      <span class="ic-badge">$99/child · All-Inclusive</span>
      <span>No venue fees. No food minimums. No wristband upcharges. What you book is what you pay.</span>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

