        </div>
        <div class="safety-item">
          <div class="si-icon">🛡️</div>
          <div class="si-body">
            <h4>Background-Checked Staff</h4>
            <p>Every team member is background-checked and trained for group supervision with kids. This is non-negotiable for us.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="safety-item">
          <div class="si-icon">👨‍👩‍👧</div>
