            <p>Kids are released only to the parent or guardian you've approved at booking. No exceptions.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="safety-item">
          <div class="si-icon">📋</div>
          <div class="si-body">
            <h4>Structured Check-Ins at Every Stop</h4>
            <p>We do a full headcount at every transition — bus boarding, venue arrival, pizza party start, and pickup. Everyone is accounted for at all times.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

