        <summary>Can we bring a birthday cake?</summary>
        <p>Absolutely! Bring a cake (or cupcakes) to the pizza party and our host will make sure there's a proper cake moment. We'll handle the rest.</p>
      </details>
      <details class="faq-item">
        <summary>How many kids can you take?</summary>
        <p>We handle groups of all sizes. The vehicle scales with your group — from smaller parties to large group events with 30+ kids. Contact us for large group pricing.</p>
      </details>
